Description: DNLI_PYRFU - Experimental evidence at protein level: Swiss-Prot protein existence level 1. DNA ligase that seals nicks in double-stranded DNA during DNA replication, DNA recombination and DNA repair. From Pyrococcus furiosus (strain ATCC 43587 / DSM 3638 / JCM 8422 / Vc1).
β-lactamase; bla; confers resistance to ampicillin, carbenicillin, and related antibiotics
transcription terminator for bacteriophage T7 RNA polymerase
bidirectional E. coli tonB-P14 transcription terminator
LacZα fragment of β-galactosidase; lacZ fragment
